GemBox.Document supports a variety of text formatting options like font name, size and color; on / off properties like bold, italic, underline, strikethrough, subscript, superscript and many others. can be set on:
elements , and ;
styles and ;
DocumentModel.DefaultCharacterFormat and ListLevelFormat.CharacterFormat properties.
For more information about properties, see character formatting example.

GemBox.Document supports a variety of paragraph formatting options like alignment, borders, spacing, indentation, tabs and many others. can be set on:
element;
style;
DocumentModel.DefaultParagraphFormat property.
For more information about properties, see paragraph formatting example.
